WEBVTT

01:35.479 --> 01:36.610
A couple of days ago,

01:36.960 --> 01:38.840
the ships didn't even dare to dock.

01:38.840 --> 01:41.920
You had to take a small boat to the middle of the river to board.

01:41.920 --> 01:42.680
Now,

01:42.680 --> 01:44.720
taking a small boat to the middle of the river

01:44.720 --> 01:45.920
costs thirty yuan.

01:46.120 --> 01:47.320
Thirty yuan?

01:48.240 --> 01:48.880
Isn't that almost

01:48.880 --> 01:49.680
one gold bar?

01:49.880 --> 01:50.680
Exactly.

01:51.080 --> 01:52.009
I'm telling you,

01:52.039 --> 01:53.300
that's today's price.

01:53.360 --> 01:53.960
Tomorrow,

01:54.000 --> 01:55.530
who knows how high it'll go.

02:02.520 --> 02:03.240
Brother,

02:04.040 --> 02:04.970
do you have a way?

02:05.680 --> 02:07.080
Yes, do you want it?

02:09.160 --> 02:10.090
Make it cheaper.

02:11.120 --> 02:12.160
I can't, brother.

02:12.320 --> 02:13.480
Not a penny less.

02:14.360 --> 02:17.160
Brother, please donate for the War of Resistance.

02:18.360 --> 02:19.640
Not a single penny.

02:22.800 --> 02:25.329
Sir, please donate for the War of Resistance.

02:25.880 --> 02:27.079
One gold bar.

02:27.760 --> 02:29.360
Are you going to give it to me?

02:33.000 --> 02:35.660
Hello. Please donate for the War of Resistance.

02:36.560 --> 02:39.220
Hello. Please donate for the War of Resistance.

02:39.440 --> 02:40.720
Here, careful.

02:41.240 --> 02:42.600
Here, water is coming.

02:42.920 --> 02:43.720
Here.

02:45.600 --> 02:46.760
Put it down.

02:47.840 --> 02:48.560
Brother.

02:48.920 --> 02:49.520
Give me a bucket of water.

02:49.520 --> 02:50.440
Here, let me.

02:53.640 --> 02:54.600
Move away.

02:54.840 --> 02:55.520
I want some too.

02:55.520 --> 02:56.160
Thank you.

02:56.440 --> 02:57.240
A little more.

02:57.240 --> 02:58.160
Fill it up.

02:58.280 --> 02:59.800
Okay, that's enough.

03:00.040 --> 03:00.600
Here.

03:00.720 --> 03:01.560
Zuliang.

03:02.120 --> 03:03.440
Director Wang.

03:03.920 --> 03:06.640
You students who joined the army on the front lines,

03:06.640 --> 03:08.440
can't just work without eating.

03:08.520 --> 03:09.440
We are not tired.

03:09.440 --> 03:10.880
Right, we are not tired. We are fine.

03:10.880 --> 03:11.960
The revolution is important,

03:11.960 --> 03:13.440
but your health is equally important.

03:13.440 --> 03:15.640
However, in view of your performance,

03:16.079 --> 03:17.600
the superiors have specially approved

03:17.600 --> 03:20.280
the rank of Second Lieutenant for all of you.

03:21.720 --> 03:22.850
Second Lieutenant!

03:22.960 --> 03:23.760
Come and see.

03:26.720 --> 03:27.680
Let me see.

03:28.040 --> 03:28.880
Is it mine?

03:29.079 --> 03:30.280
This is a new uniform.

03:30.520 --> 03:31.440
Is it ours?

03:31.880 --> 03:33.360
My name is even written here.

03:33.360 --> 03:34.880
Then I'll be a Second Lieutenant from now on.

03:34.880 --> 03:35.880
You are too.

03:37.720 --> 03:38.880
This looks so sharp.

03:39.120 --> 03:40.050
How impressive.

03:40.400 --> 03:41.440
We have some

03:41.800 --> 03:43.800
new uniforms left in our warehouse,

03:44.000 --> 03:45.930
consider it a bargain for you guys.

03:46.560 --> 03:47.420
Director Wang.

03:47.880 --> 03:49.320
Then we...

03:50.800 --> 03:51.460
Try them on.

03:51.840 --> 03:53.360
Let's go.

04:07.520 --> 04:08.850
Come, let Daddy hug you.

04:11.640 --> 04:12.970
Hold it well, it's warm.

04:15.560 --> 04:17.519
Rock, paper, scissors.

04:17.760 --> 04:18.519
Old man,

04:18.640 --> 04:20.170
do you want a foreign watch?

04:21.760 --> 04:22.890
Look, it's elegant.

04:22.920 --> 04:24.000
Go away.

04:25.000 --> 04:26.200
Wait, I need to buy a ticket

04:26.200 --> 04:26.840
to Hankou.

04:28.040 --> 04:29.080
What are you doing here?

04:29.080 --> 04:30.280
No money for a ticket.

04:30.520 --> 04:31.080
Get out of here!

04:31.080 --> 04:33.080
Write us a letter when you get there!

04:35.200 --> 04:36.659
Newspapers! Newspapers!

04:38.800 --> 04:40.040
Water for sale!

04:43.320 --> 04:45.480
Newspapers! Newspapers!

04:46.000 --> 04:46.800
Excuse me,

04:48.280 --> 04:50.540
Hold your luggage carefully. Watch out.

04:50.760 --> 04:51.680
Excuse me.

04:51.920 --> 04:53.000
Is the boat to Wuhan

04:53.080 --> 04:54.340
checking tickets now?

04:54.480 --> 04:56.610
There are no more boats to Wuhan today.

04:56.640 --> 04:58.320
Have you seen a little brother,

04:58.320 --> 04:59.250
about this tall,

04:59.320 --> 05:01.050
with a big patch on his clothes?

05:02.080 --> 05:03.410
Your ticket is checked.

05:08.480 --> 05:09.840
Please open the door!

05:10.040 --> 05:11.480
Are there any tickets left?

05:11.480 --> 05:12.520
What are you doing?

05:12.520 --> 05:13.440
Stop!

05:19.120 --> 05:20.120
I told you to stop!

05:22.440 --> 05:24.160
Stop!

05:25.800 --> 05:27.460
Don't think I can't catch you!

05:29.240 --> 05:30.120
No rush.

05:30.240 --> 05:31.040
Come, line up first.

05:31.040 --> 05:32.300
Take out your tickets.

05:33.200 --> 05:34.280
Hold your ticket.

05:44.680 --> 05:46.040
Read the newspaper!

05:46.200 --> 05:48.640
Brigade Commander Zhang Yunkui disobeyed orders.

05:48.640 --> 05:51.280
Dachang is lost, the whole situation is trapped.

05:51.280 --> 05:52.480
Newspapers!

05:52.840 --> 05:54.280
Sir, newspaper.

05:54.920 --> 05:56.320
Read the newspaper!

05:56.680 --> 05:58.760
The entire 87th Brigade is held accountable.

05:58.760 --> 06:01.040
The runaway general is to blame.

06:01.240 --> 06:02.640
Newspapers!

06:03.240 --> 06:04.040
Brigade Commander Zhang Yunkui.

06:04.040 --> 06:04.800
We will donate too.

06:04.800 --> 06:05.480
Thank you for your support.

06:05.480 --> 06:06.960
Kill a few more Japanese.

06:06.960 --> 06:07.480
Thank you.

06:07.480 --> 06:09.810
Where did this runaway general come from?

06:09.920 --> 06:12.440
Once Dachang is lost, everything is lost.

06:13.760 --> 06:14.400
Sir,

06:14.920 --> 06:16.200
the survival of the nation is at stake.

06:16.200 --> 06:18.640
Please contribute to the war of resistance.

06:18.640 --> 06:19.100
Donate.

06:19.240 --> 06:19.720
Donate.

06:20.320 --> 06:21.180
Thank you, sir.

06:21.800 --> 06:22.680
Thank you, sir.

06:23.520 --> 06:24.240
Thank you.

06:24.520 --> 06:25.040
I'll donate too.

06:25.040 --> 06:25.720
Thank you, ma'am.

06:25.720 --> 06:26.960
We must support the war of resistance.

06:26.960 --> 06:27.600
Thank you.

06:27.760 --> 06:28.690
I'll donate too.

06:28.720 --> 06:29.580
Thank you, sir.

06:30.000 --> 06:31.200
Thank you for your support of the war of resistance.

06:31.200 --> 06:31.760
Have to support it.

06:31.760 --> 06:32.360
Thank you.

06:32.480 --> 06:33.560
You are very righteous, sir.

06:33.560 --> 06:34.840
China will win!

06:35.000 --> 06:36.080
Thank you.

06:41.159 --> 06:41.880
Coward!

06:42.000 --> 06:42.640
Traitor!

06:42.800 --> 06:43.680
Traitor!

06:44.320 --> 06:46.080
The Japanese haven't even arrived,

06:46.080 --> 06:47.340
and you ran away first!

06:47.360 --> 06:49.000
Leaving us civilians behind,

06:49.000 --> 06:50.400
this is treason!

06:52.960 --> 06:53.320
You!

06:53.440 --> 06:54.040
Traitor!

06:54.159 --> 06:55.040
Defending the country,

06:55.040 --> 06:56.360
is it worth doing this?

06:56.840 --> 06:57.240
Deserter!

06:57.240 --> 06:58.159
You are a soldier.

06:58.159 --> 06:58.680
What are you doing?

06:58.680 --> 07:00.210
You are paid by the country!

07:01.000 --> 07:01.360
What kind of people are they?

07:01.360 --> 07:03.360
Great-grandfather, let's go home.

07:03.600 --> 07:04.480
I'll clean it up right away.

07:04.480 --> 07:05.880
What a bunch of bastards.

07:06.760 --> 07:07.600
Shut up!

07:07.840 --> 07:09.760
Our young master is risking his life at the frontline,

07:09.760 --> 07:11.360
protecting people like you.

07:11.600 --> 07:13.060
You are the real traitors!

07:13.080 --> 07:14.080
Your conscience

07:14.320 --> 07:15.880
has been eaten by the Japs.

07:17.200 --> 07:18.130
Don't you agree?

07:18.640 --> 07:19.520
Don't tear it.

07:20.960 --> 07:23.090
Whoever pasted it should tear it down.

07:24.680 --> 07:27.360
Whoever threw it should clean it up

07:27.760 --> 07:29.240
and apologize to me in person.

07:29.240 --> 07:30.320
It's clearly written in the newspaper.

07:30.320 --> 07:31.200
Great-grandfather,

07:31.200 --> 07:32.260
still so stubborn.

07:32.440 --> 07:33.120
Shameless.

07:33.360 --> 07:35.360
Where are you going, Great-grandfather?

07:35.360 --> 07:36.840
Nationalist Government.

07:53.560 --> 07:55.760
I thought you had already left the city.

07:58.480 --> 07:59.960
That high-ranking official,

07:59.960 --> 08:01.520
he pointed a gun at my head.

08:02.000 --> 08:03.120
He threatened me,

08:03.360 --> 08:05.890
saying I can never see the Zhang family again.

08:06.200 --> 08:07.730
Of course I'm afraid to die.

08:08.760 --> 08:09.960
I even got to the pier.

08:10.160 --> 08:12.620
But as soon as I got there, I thought about it.

08:12.960 --> 08:14.880
There must be something going on.

08:15.120 --> 08:17.050
That official must be up to no good.

08:18.160 --> 08:19.160
Then I remembered

08:19.680 --> 08:22.040
our Brigade Commander saved my life.

08:22.320 --> 08:24.320
I can't be that heartless.

08:28.040 --> 08:30.320
Thank you, Brother Wanfu.

08:31.480 --> 08:32.640
But that official,

08:33.200 --> 08:34.600
he sounded so scary.

08:37.440 --> 08:38.559
Come home with me.

08:39.159 --> 08:40.280
I will protect you.

08:40.919 --> 08:42.850
I won't let them lay a finger on you.

09:12.680 --> 09:13.680
Keep it straight.

09:15.960 --> 09:16.960
Keep it straight.

09:24.040 --> 09:25.300
It's been ten minutes.

09:25.720 --> 09:27.480
Holding it for fifteen minutes without spilling a drop

09:27.480 --> 09:28.740
is just too difficult.

09:28.880 --> 09:31.740
The most important thing in surgery is steadiness.

09:31.760 --> 09:32.760
Keep it straight.

10:13.560 --> 10:14.520
Brother Yunkui

10:14.960 --> 10:16.080
is awake.

10:23.800 --> 10:25.460
I'll go get him some porridge.

10:28.880 --> 10:30.320
Zuliang,

10:30.600 --> 10:32.240
it's me, Brother Yunkui.

10:32.600 --> 10:33.960
You saved me.

10:42.720 --> 10:46.160
This is Liu Town.

10:46.960 --> 10:48.690
This is the military hospital.

10:48.920 --> 10:50.380
I am a military doctor now.

10:54.760 --> 10:55.840
Dachang.

10:58.000 --> 10:59.440
Dachang.

11:01.080 --> 11:02.080
Dachang.

11:03.320 --> 11:03.960
It's lost.

11:18.120 --> 11:20.600
Brother Yunkui, you survived.

11:21.280 --> 11:22.880
Don't think too much for now.

11:23.040 --> 11:26.500
The doctor said you need to stay in bed for at least half a month.

11:36.200 --> 11:38.680
You must tell me clearly

11:38.680 --> 11:39.080
Go.

11:39.080 --> 11:40.140
what a deserter is.

11:40.640 --> 11:41.480
Get out of here.

11:41.480 --> 11:42.960
My son, Zhang Yunkui,

11:43.520 --> 11:45.040
Zhang Yunkui is innocent!

11:45.600 --> 11:47.930
We have both human and physical evidence.

11:48.040 --> 11:48.640
Hurry up.

11:48.800 --> 11:50.960
You can't just talk nonsense!

11:51.680 --> 11:53.600
You all fled to the rear,

11:54.000 --> 11:56.120
and Chairman Chiang also fled.

11:56.720 --> 11:58.640
You are the real deserters!

11:59.320 --> 12:02.120
My son died in battle on the Shanghai Battlefield,

12:02.240 --> 12:04.040
and his body isn't even cold yet.

12:04.080 --> 12:06.480
And you slander him in the newspapers!

12:06.920 --> 12:08.920
You put the word 'deserter'

12:09.160 --> 12:12.280
on soldiers who died in battle.

12:12.720 --> 12:14.960
You are destroying his reputation after his death!

12:14.960 --> 12:15.200
Go!

12:15.280 --> 12:16.520
What are you two good for?

12:16.520 --> 12:17.080
Drag him away.

12:17.080 --> 12:17.610
Yes, sir.

12:17.640 --> 12:19.640
You are destroying his reputation!

12:19.680 --> 12:22.160
Liao Fengnian! Sun Huaiyi!

12:22.440 --> 12:22.880
Madam.

12:22.880 --> 12:23.800
He Yingqin!

12:23.800 --> 12:24.400
Great-grandfather is over there.

12:24.400 --> 12:24.960
Dad.

12:25.200 --> 12:26.200
Chiang Kai-shek!

12:26.680 --> 12:27.400
Come out, all of you!

12:27.400 --> 12:28.440
Great-grandfather!

12:28.440 --> 12:29.880
I want to confront them!

12:30.200 --> 12:32.280
Who is the fleeing general?

12:32.320 --> 12:32.520
Great-grandfather.

12:32.520 --> 12:34.200
Why did you come here, Dad?

12:35.440 --> 12:36.520
Little brother,

12:36.920 --> 12:38.240
you're back.

12:38.920 --> 12:40.640
You came back at the right time.

12:40.640 --> 12:41.360
I'm back.

12:41.720 --> 12:43.250
I went to the Ministry of War

12:43.400 --> 12:45.320
to seek justice for Yunkui,

12:45.680 --> 12:47.120
but they wouldn't let me in.

12:47.120 --> 12:48.320
I could only come to

12:48.320 --> 12:51.880
the highest Nationalist Government to appeal,

12:52.280 --> 12:54.640
but they still wouldn't let me in!

12:55.000 --> 12:56.320
Look at these words.

12:56.760 --> 12:58.680
Nationalist Government.

12:59.000 --> 13:00.640
Whose nation are you?

13:00.880 --> 13:02.340
Whose people do you serve?

13:02.440 --> 13:04.000
Whose government are you?

13:05.240 --> 13:05.920
Perfect.

13:06.200 --> 13:07.240
We have a witness.

13:07.480 --> 13:08.280
Come in with me

13:08.560 --> 13:09.960
and reason with them.

13:10.560 --> 13:11.360
Great-grandfather.

13:11.360 --> 13:12.160
Dad, we can't go.

13:12.160 --> 13:13.200
You can't.

13:13.200 --> 13:14.880
Dad, look at this Nationalist Government.

13:14.880 --> 13:16.680
It's already in such a mess.

13:17.040 --> 13:18.920
They don't even know where they are going.

13:18.920 --> 13:20.980
What's the point of looking for them?

13:21.640 --> 13:21.840
Yujiao.

13:21.840 --> 13:24.040
Even if you smash your head on the ground now,

13:24.040 --> 13:25.200
just like Yang Jiye

13:25.200 --> 13:26.360
who hit his head on Li Ling's Stele,

13:26.360 --> 13:28.480
no one will listen to you.

13:31.120 --> 13:32.520
Yujiao,

13:33.240 --> 13:35.320
this is Liao Fengnian's conspiracy.

13:35.640 --> 13:38.120
They suffered a crushing defeat on the front line,

13:38.120 --> 13:39.320
and they put the blame

13:39.360 --> 13:41.880
on our Yunkui.

13:42.280 --> 13:43.480
You said it yourself,

13:43.680 --> 13:45.080
they intentionally put the blame

13:45.080 --> 13:46.360
on Yunkui.

13:47.000 --> 13:49.400
Then why should we clash with them head-on?

13:51.280 --> 13:53.480
Father, we can go to the newspaper.

13:53.840 --> 13:55.200
They don't listen to us.

13:55.360 --> 13:57.600
If we publish it, someone will listen.

13:57.880 --> 13:58.960
Let's use the power of public opinion

13:58.960 --> 14:00.520
to clear Yunkui's name, okay?

14:00.520 --> 14:01.320
Yes.

14:01.600 --> 14:04.130
I can also testify for our Brigade Commander.

14:05.800 --> 14:06.920
You are right.

14:07.120 --> 14:09.360
You are calmer than me.

14:09.720 --> 14:11.250
They turn black into white,

14:11.360 --> 14:13.090
committing countless crimes.

14:13.320 --> 14:15.450
I will write a complaint when I go back.

14:15.960 --> 14:18.080
I will send it to all the newspapers.

14:18.520 --> 14:20.640
I will announce it to the world.

14:21.000 --> 14:21.920
Let's go back.

14:25.200 --> 14:26.660
Nationalist Government.

14:26.920 --> 14:28.440
So big.

15:58.560 --> 16:01.240
Father, the meal is ready.

16:04.120 --> 16:04.980
Where is Wanfu?

16:06.160 --> 16:07.000
Here.

16:07.080 --> 16:08.610
It's good that you are here.

16:08.840 --> 16:10.240
With you as a witness,

16:10.680 --> 16:12.200
there is still hope

16:12.480 --> 16:13.720
for Yunkui's matter.

16:15.720 --> 16:17.080
Yes.

16:17.600 --> 16:19.640
Then Great-grandfather, let's eat.

16:19.640 --> 16:20.840
Before doing anything,

16:20.840 --> 16:21.800
we must eat.

16:22.080 --> 16:22.680
Come.

16:22.800 --> 16:24.360
Let's eat.

16:28.720 --> 16:29.480
Let me do it.

16:29.960 --> 16:30.890
I'm good at this.

16:31.400 --> 16:32.760
We can't let the guest do it,

16:32.760 --> 16:34.040
it's the rule.

16:37.040 --> 16:38.160
Wanfu.

16:38.600 --> 16:40.640
What is China?

16:43.400 --> 16:44.600
Great-grandfather,

16:44.640 --> 16:46.800
you really stumped me.

16:47.320 --> 16:48.400
Is it called China

16:50.040 --> 16:51.800
because we are in the middle?

16:51.800 --> 16:52.920
Is that why?

16:54.000 --> 16:55.460
We are the Chinese nation,

16:55.680 --> 16:58.480
including Han, Manchu, Mongol, Hui, and Tibetan.

16:58.880 --> 17:01.000
We share a common Chinese culture.

17:01.720 --> 17:03.360
Well said.

17:05.480 --> 17:06.920
Only culture

17:07.520 --> 17:10.040
is the foundation of a nation.

17:11.599 --> 17:12.680
Not guns.

17:13.119 --> 17:14.400
Not emperors,

17:14.800 --> 17:16.280
nor the name of the state.

17:16.920 --> 17:18.579
Before the Republic of China,

17:18.680 --> 17:21.800
China existed for five thousand years.

17:22.240 --> 17:25.040
Through countless dynastic changes,

17:25.560 --> 17:27.760
culture has not died.

17:28.119 --> 17:31.680
It survives and continues.

17:32.600 --> 17:34.760
This is culture.

17:36.680 --> 17:38.280
Wanfu,

17:39.840 --> 17:41.200
do you understand?

17:42.880 --> 17:43.480
No.

17:44.600 --> 17:45.760
Great-grandfather,

17:45.760 --> 17:46.960
I am a person

17:47.000 --> 17:48.720
with no culture at all.

17:49.000 --> 17:51.600
I barely know any words.

17:52.120 --> 17:53.120
No.

17:53.480 --> 17:54.680
You do.

17:54.920 --> 17:57.280
Culture is not about how many words you know,

17:57.280 --> 17:59.000
nor just about books.

17:59.440 --> 18:02.040
Culture is a thought of conscience.

18:02.880 --> 18:04.000
Wanfu,

18:04.320 --> 18:06.560
you delivered the sword for Yunkui,

18:06.800 --> 18:10.320
and risked your life to testify for him.

18:10.480 --> 18:13.320
This shows you have a conscience,

18:13.600 --> 18:15.060
and a heart of compassion.

18:15.240 --> 18:17.560
This is the culture of our nation.

18:19.440 --> 18:23.240
Yunkui is very lucky.

18:24.760 --> 18:28.720
To have a comrade and brother like you.

18:29.240 --> 18:30.920
Our Zhang family

18:34.560 --> 18:35.360
thanks you.

18:35.880 --> 18:37.000
Great-grandfather, please don't.

18:37.000 --> 18:37.520
This...

18:37.520 --> 18:38.640
Isn't this messing up the seniority?

18:38.640 --> 18:40.280
How can we call each other brothers?

18:40.280 --> 18:41.840
My father means

18:41.920 --> 18:43.520
you and Yunkui are brothers.

18:46.760 --> 18:48.120
Then I and Brigade Commander Zhang

18:48.120 --> 18:49.520
are naturally brothers.

18:50.520 --> 18:51.080
I

18:51.280 --> 18:52.480
vouch for my brother.

18:52.800 --> 18:54.760
That's only right

18:55.680 --> 18:56.640
and proper.

18:57.120 --> 18:58.520
It's what should be done.

19:09.320 --> 19:10.200
Great-grandfather.

19:10.200 --> 19:11.240
Come here.

19:11.480 --> 19:12.360
Actually,

19:13.080 --> 19:15.480
let me tell you the truth.

19:15.800 --> 19:17.720
Please don't flatter me.

19:19.000 --> 19:20.440
I really

19:24.000 --> 19:25.440
can't stay here long.

19:29.440 --> 19:30.040
It's like this.

19:30.040 --> 19:31.600
I came back today

19:31.800 --> 19:32.880
also because

19:33.680 --> 19:35.200
I have to go to Wuhan.

19:35.760 --> 19:36.620
You don't know.

19:36.680 --> 19:38.360
I have a fiancée.

19:38.600 --> 19:39.520
She is in Wuhan now.

19:39.520 --> 19:41.850
She doesn't even know if I'm alive or dead.

19:42.000 --> 19:43.600
I'm really afraid she isn't waiting for me anymore.

19:43.600 --> 19:45.400
So I have to hurry over there.

19:45.880 --> 19:46.940
But you don't know,

19:47.080 --> 19:48.410
I went to the pier today.

19:48.880 --> 19:49.810
The ticket price

19:49.840 --> 19:51.240
changes every day.

19:51.360 --> 19:52.360
Every single day.

19:52.480 --> 19:53.320
I...

19:53.440 --> 19:54.440
the money in my pocket...

19:54.440 --> 19:56.680
It's really

19:57.000 --> 19:58.240
just

20:01.320 --> 20:02.440
not enough.

20:09.080 --> 20:10.400
Not enough.

20:20.480 --> 20:21.120
Nurse,

20:21.200 --> 20:23.240
we are reporters from the Anti-Enemy Backup Society.

20:23.240 --> 20:24.920
We want to interview the wounded here,

20:24.920 --> 20:25.920
take some photos,

20:26.040 --> 20:27.970
and publicize their heroic deeds.

20:28.240 --> 20:29.970
Could you help introduce them?

20:30.600 --> 20:31.440
Okay.

20:33.400 --> 20:34.930
Squad Leader, Zhang Guifu.

20:35.240 --> 20:36.800
He always charged at the front.

20:36.800 --> 20:38.730
He's the best at bayonet fighting.

20:40.440 --> 20:40.880
Come.

20:40.880 --> 20:43.280
Three, two, one.

20:46.080 --> 20:48.120
Private First Class, Deng Guanghui.

20:48.120 --> 20:50.780
He was burned like this when saving the wounded.

20:52.400 --> 20:53.960
One, two, three.

20:56.560 --> 20:57.960
Private, Yu Chengjie.

20:58.160 --> 21:00.290
He went to blow up tanks with grenades,

21:00.360 --> 21:01.480
both hands...

21:03.480 --> 21:04.680
Let's take a picture.

21:05.080 --> 21:06.160
Come.

21:06.880 --> 21:08.960
Three, two, one.

21:09.280 --> 21:10.610
Company Commander Qin.

21:11.240 --> 21:12.570
Company Commander Qin.

21:12.880 --> 21:13.760
It's not lit.

21:14.600 --> 21:15.920
You can enjoy it even without lighting it.

21:15.920 --> 21:17.600
One puff and it won't hurt.

21:17.880 --> 21:18.810
Have some water.

21:19.160 --> 21:20.480
Water will help you.

21:22.920 --> 21:23.400
Thank you, Nurse.

21:23.400 --> 21:25.360
Little kid.

21:59.920 --> 22:00.680
Father,

22:01.320 --> 22:03.780
Liao Fengnian sent someone to deliver this.

22:18.080 --> 22:19.240
What a villain.

22:20.000 --> 22:21.960
He's two-faced and heartless.

22:22.320 --> 22:24.720
It's entirely an excuse to stall and dodge.

22:32.000 --> 22:33.680
The superiors have classified Yunkui

22:33.680 --> 22:34.760
as absent without leave,

22:34.760 --> 22:35.760
not as a deserter.

22:35.960 --> 22:37.640
He blamed all the rights, wrongs, and problems

22:37.640 --> 22:39.100
on the tabloid reporters,

22:39.800 --> 22:42.320
saying they exaggerated.

22:42.600 --> 22:44.960
He is obviously Yunkui's friend.

22:45.520 --> 22:47.520
He should have come forward to testify

22:47.520 --> 22:48.800
and stand up for him.

22:49.640 --> 22:52.770
Instead, he found an excuse to run back to the frontline.

22:53.120 --> 22:54.320
This is unrighteous.

22:54.560 --> 22:57.320
He's clearly a coward.

23:10.680 --> 23:11.520
He also sent us

23:11.520 --> 23:13.240
three boat tickets to Wuhan.

23:13.960 --> 23:15.240
Petty favors.

23:16.320 --> 23:17.840
He is just trying to cover it up,

23:17.840 --> 23:20.520
afraid I'll go make a scene at the Nanjing government.

23:20.520 --> 23:22.000
I cannot accept this.

23:26.560 --> 23:27.240
Father,

23:27.960 --> 23:29.880
when Yunkui left, he told us

23:30.160 --> 23:32.240
to be ready to go to Wuhan.

23:34.320 --> 23:36.960
Now, all the news from the frontline is bad.

23:37.200 --> 23:39.560
Everyone in Nanjing is fleeing.

23:39.640 --> 23:40.760
You can also see

23:40.960 --> 23:42.560
that the military and government officials

23:42.560 --> 23:43.920
are also retreating.

23:44.280 --> 23:46.440
Now, boat tickets from Nanjing to the rear

23:46.440 --> 23:47.770
change prices every day

23:48.200 --> 23:49.280
and are hard to get.

23:49.400 --> 23:51.400
If we miss this boat...

23:53.120 --> 23:54.280
Yujiao.

23:55.240 --> 23:56.080
We can't be bought

23:56.080 --> 23:58.160
by these three boat tickets.

23:58.560 --> 24:00.440
Fleeing silently as refugees,

24:00.920 --> 24:04.080
silently bearing Yunkui's injustice.

24:04.600 --> 24:06.260
Nanjing has a million people,

24:06.440 --> 24:08.040
they won't all run away.

24:08.400 --> 24:11.080
If I don't clear Yunkui's name

24:11.240 --> 24:12.760
and wash away the injustice,

24:12.760 --> 24:15.020
I won't take a single step out of Nanjing.

24:16.520 --> 24:17.850
Liao Fengnian ran away,

24:17.920 --> 24:19.250
and Sun Huaiyi ran away.

24:19.280 --> 24:20.720
I will use public opinion

24:20.720 --> 24:21.960
to seek justice.

24:22.160 --> 24:24.320
I will submit articles to all the newspaper offices.

24:24.320 --> 24:25.760
I want to find a place

24:25.840 --> 24:28.520
to get justice for Yunkui.

24:38.440 --> 24:39.560
Yujiao.

24:40.080 --> 24:40.760
Dad.

24:40.760 --> 24:41.760
How about

24:42.120 --> 24:44.980
having Mrs. Liu accompany you back to our hometown?

24:46.320 --> 24:47.240
Dad.

24:49.000 --> 24:51.520
When the war just started, Yunkui told me,

24:52.600 --> 24:54.160
no matter what happens,

24:54.520 --> 24:56.520
our family shouldn't be separated.

24:56.800 --> 24:58.560
My parents died a long time ago.

24:59.240 --> 25:01.570
Which hometown do you want me to return to?

25:05.720 --> 25:07.120
You decide.

25:08.320 --> 25:09.720
I'll listen to you.

25:11.760 --> 25:12.840
Okay.

25:15.640 --> 25:17.200
I'll continue writing.

25:40.880 --> 25:42.680
Where is Wanfu?

25:47.080 --> 25:48.520
You don't know either.

25:57.680 --> 25:59.200
You don't know either.

26:12.800 --> 26:14.600
Wanfu.

26:20.800 --> 26:22.600
Where are you?

26:26.200 --> 26:27.080
Mrs. Liu.

26:27.960 --> 26:30.280
The three of the Yang family next door all left.

26:30.280 --> 26:32.120
They bought tickets from the black market.

26:32.120 --> 26:34.240
The situation is getting more tense by the day.

26:34.240 --> 26:35.120
Master holds

26:35.120 --> 26:36.680
3 tickets to Wuhan,

26:36.960 --> 26:37.800
but he just won't leave.

26:37.800 --> 26:38.880
What should we do?

26:40.600 --> 26:42.840
Those Japanese planes come every day now.

26:42.840 --> 26:43.720
When the alarm goes off,

26:43.720 --> 26:44.520
where can you hide

26:44.520 --> 26:45.640
on a boat?

26:47.080 --> 26:49.000
Didn't you listen to the radio yesterday?

26:49.000 --> 26:50.200
A boat in Jiujiang

26:50.360 --> 26:51.560
was bombed and sunk.

26:52.000 --> 26:53.480
It's terrifying.

26:55.480 --> 26:56.680
Yi.

26:57.440 --> 26:58.800
What do you think?

26:59.600 --> 27:00.320
Does it fit?

27:01.440 --> 27:02.400
Thank you.

27:05.000 --> 27:05.800
Do you know

27:06.160 --> 27:07.640
the safest way to flee?

27:09.000 --> 27:09.720
I don't know.

27:09.720 --> 27:10.720
By walking.

27:11.040 --> 27:13.120
And you must avoid highways and take small paths.

27:13.120 --> 27:14.780
Highways are too big a target.

27:15.320 --> 27:16.560
Have you ever seen a bombing?

27:16.560 --> 27:17.490
Of course I have.

27:17.920 --> 27:19.980
We run from air raid sirens every day.

27:20.800 --> 27:21.880
Your running from sirens

27:21.880 --> 27:23.040
is completely useless.

27:23.040 --> 27:24.570
It's not worth mentioning.

27:25.160 --> 27:26.490
Let me tell you about it.

27:28.720 --> 27:29.640
Let me tell you,

27:30.800 --> 27:32.480
those Japanese planes.

27:33.160 --> 27:34.200
Look.

27:34.480 --> 27:35.410
With their wings

27:35.920 --> 27:36.920
tilted like this,

27:38.560 --> 27:40.080
they dive down

27:43.120 --> 27:44.800
and fly right over your scalp.

27:45.480 --> 27:46.360
You know?

27:46.680 --> 27:48.200
Then suddenly,

27:49.440 --> 27:50.170
they pull up.

27:50.320 --> 27:52.000
They pull up and climb.

27:52.120 --> 27:53.240
Boom,

27:53.440 --> 27:54.170
a bomb drops.

27:54.880 --> 27:55.880
Boom,

27:56.120 --> 27:57.250
a second bomb drops.

27:57.280 --> 27:58.680
Followed immediately by

28:00.720 --> 28:02.960
a gust of hot wind,

28:04.160 --> 28:05.840
hitting you like a door.

28:06.760 --> 28:08.360
Then you can't see anything.

28:08.960 --> 28:12.360
All you see is smoke and ash.

28:13.120 --> 28:15.640
Blood and torn flesh

28:16.120 --> 28:18.160
fall all over you.

28:20.400 --> 28:21.280
Let me tell you.

28:21.960 --> 28:23.090
Nanjing was bombed,

28:23.320 --> 28:25.520
so Wuhan will definitely be bombed too.

28:25.960 --> 28:26.800
The Japanese.

28:27.280 --> 28:29.240
They specifically target crowded places.

28:29.240 --> 28:30.080
Big cities.

28:30.240 --> 28:32.240
Places with industry and commerce.

28:32.560 --> 28:34.420
Do you know where they don't bomb?

28:34.760 --> 28:35.490
I don't know.

28:36.520 --> 28:38.080
They don't bomb the countryside.

28:38.080 --> 28:39.120
What's the point of bombing

28:39.120 --> 28:40.000
a hole in a cabbage field?

28:40.000 --> 28:41.240
Bombs cost money too.

28:42.200 --> 28:43.160
Exactly.

28:43.440 --> 28:44.840
It's better to quit earlier

28:44.840 --> 28:46.300
and go to the countryside.

28:46.400 --> 28:47.480
Yeah.

28:49.400 --> 28:50.280
Yi.

28:51.560 --> 28:52.360
Come and help.

28:52.480 --> 28:53.640
Okay.

29:02.720 --> 29:03.640
Yi.

29:04.240 --> 29:05.000
Do you know

29:05.400 --> 29:06.600
what it looks like when a piece of shrapnel

29:06.600 --> 29:08.040
hits a head?

29:09.080 --> 29:10.320
Just like this.

29:10.800 --> 29:12.880
The white brains come pouring out.

29:13.280 --> 29:15.040
The worst is being shot in the stomach,

29:15.040 --> 29:17.370
intestines spilling all over the ground.

29:18.760 --> 29:20.020
You are so disgusting.

29:27.960 --> 29:29.240
I can see

29:29.640 --> 29:30.280
you

29:30.760 --> 29:33.090
just want to scare Yi and me out of our wits,

29:33.280 --> 29:35.240
so we'll both be scared back to the countryside,

29:35.240 --> 29:36.080
right?

29:36.640 --> 29:38.560
You are coveting the Old Master's

29:38.560 --> 29:39.690
three boat tickets.

29:40.760 --> 29:42.820
What are you talking about, Mrs. Liu?

29:43.480 --> 29:45.960
I'm just telling Yi what I saw with my own eyes.

29:45.960 --> 29:47.640
Don't be so petty.

29:48.120 --> 29:49.840
I don't know if I'm petty or not.

29:49.840 --> 29:51.000
Let me be clear.

29:51.520 --> 29:52.760
I am all alone.

29:52.960 --> 29:54.520
I've been in the Zhang family for decades.

29:54.520 --> 29:56.050
The Zhang family is my home.

29:56.520 --> 29:58.400
Anyway, I will stick closely to Madam.

29:58.400 --> 30:00.000
Madam is about to give birth.

30:00.280 --> 30:01.000
I,

30:01.760 --> 30:02.640
no matter what,

30:03.200 --> 30:04.280
will never quit.

30:06.040 --> 30:07.200
I won't quit.

30:30.960 --> 30:33.200
Father, you're back.

30:38.080 --> 30:39.640
If you don't eat a bite,

30:39.880 --> 30:41.740
your body won't be able to take it.

30:45.080 --> 30:46.520
Let me go heat it up for you.

30:46.520 --> 30:48.320
You should eat at least a little.

30:49.520 --> 30:50.520
Yujiao.

30:51.560 --> 30:52.840
Sit down.

31:08.000 --> 31:11.800
My son Yunkui, courtesy name Xingwu,

31:12.680 --> 31:15.120
a native of Haiwen, Jiangsu,

31:16.080 --> 31:19.280
born in the 31st year of Guangxu.

31:19.560 --> 31:21.360
He lost his mother at six,

31:21.880 --> 31:23.960
but always strove to be strong.

31:24.680 --> 31:26.360
You died,

31:26.680 --> 31:28.940
and I could not bring you home for burial.

31:29.120 --> 31:30.600
Your name is disgraced,

31:30.880 --> 31:33.200
and I have nowhere to clear your name.

31:34.200 --> 31:35.480
You gallantly

31:35.920 --> 31:37.240
died for our country.

31:38.080 --> 31:41.080
Yet I hesitate, not knowing whether to stay or go.

31:42.000 --> 31:44.640
Alas, the court has lost its way,

31:45.280 --> 31:47.010
with wolves blocking the path.

31:47.320 --> 31:49.080
They shirked their duties

31:49.360 --> 31:52.440
and made you bear the blame and execution.

31:53.280 --> 31:54.120
Sorrow!

31:54.160 --> 31:56.890
No sorrow is greater than a father losing his son.

31:57.560 --> 31:58.480
Hatred!

31:58.480 --> 31:59.810
No hatred is deeper than

31:59.960 --> 32:01.620
the strong bullying the weak.

32:02.120 --> 32:04.000
Black and white are reversed

32:04.320 --> 32:05.560
by those in power.

32:05.760 --> 32:07.680
Right and wrong are blurred

32:07.800 --> 32:08.880
for the commoners.

32:10.000 --> 32:11.520
Oh, heaven above,

32:11.880 --> 32:13.480
why did you kill my good man?

32:14.360 --> 32:15.640
Two months ago,

32:16.320 --> 32:18.580
you brought me medicine before you left.

32:19.040 --> 32:20.840
Your earnest tugging at my clothes

32:20.840 --> 32:22.640
is still vivid in my mind.

32:23.280 --> 32:28.360
I still look up to Yan Zhenqing and Zheng Banqiao.

32:29.360 --> 32:30.840
Rivers are wide and deep,

32:31.640 --> 32:33.370
deer and apes gather together.

32:33.920 --> 32:37.840
Oh, souls, feel no sorrow or fear.

32:38.720 --> 32:43.080
But your wife is expecting and hasn't given birth to a son yet.

32:44.080 --> 32:46.520
How dare I die?

32:46.760 --> 32:47.840
Alas,

32:48.120 --> 32:51.520
if you have a spirit, could you tell me?

32:53.240 --> 32:56.600
Alas, it hurts!

32:56.880 --> 32:59.560
Alas, it hurts!

33:05.360 --> 33:08.640
Today I will send it to the 'Central Daily News'.

33:09.200 --> 33:10.730
If they dare not publish it,

33:10.760 --> 33:12.480
I will print a few more copies,

33:12.920 --> 33:14.780
'Morning Post', 'Evening News'.

33:14.920 --> 33:15.760
I don't believe

33:15.760 --> 33:18.120
there is no place to reason in Nanjing.

33:40.800 --> 33:41.720
Yi,

33:42.080 --> 33:44.240
are you really running back to your hometown in the country?

33:44.240 --> 33:46.120
Don't listen to Wanfu trying to scare you.

33:46.120 --> 33:47.680
There are only three boat tickets.

33:47.680 --> 33:49.540
I'd better go back to the country.

33:53.280 --> 33:54.400
Slow down.

33:55.000 --> 33:56.080
Let me help.

33:56.080 --> 33:57.120
No need.

34:00.160 --> 34:01.240
Mrs. Liu,

34:01.600 --> 34:02.520
I need to discuss something with you.

34:02.520 --> 34:03.360
No.

34:03.960 --> 34:04.840
I haven't said anything yet,

34:04.840 --> 34:06.500
and you're already saying no?

34:06.760 --> 34:07.320
No.

34:07.520 --> 34:08.679
I...

34:10.199 --> 34:11.159
Madam.

34:12.159 --> 34:14.840
Great-grandfather hasn't eaten anything at all.

34:14.840 --> 34:16.170
I'll go heat it up again.

34:16.600 --> 34:17.480
Yi,

34:18.040 --> 34:19.719
bring those two dishes over too,

34:19.719 --> 34:20.880
I'll heat them up together.

34:20.880 --> 34:21.440
Here.

34:25.960 --> 34:27.080
I see,

34:27.400 --> 34:29.199
these two share the same temper.

34:29.520 --> 34:30.780
Madam, you don't know.

34:30.840 --> 34:32.159
When we were on the battlefield,

34:32.159 --> 34:34.239
our Brigade Commander was either looking at the map,

34:34.239 --> 34:35.199
thinking about things,

34:35.199 --> 34:36.460
or making phone calls.

34:36.679 --> 34:38.480
He'd be busy for days and nights,

34:38.719 --> 34:40.380
and he wouldn't eat anything.

34:40.400 --> 34:41.639
So he got internal heat,

34:41.639 --> 34:43.560
and his mouth was full of blisters.

34:43.560 --> 34:45.820
Later, I used winter melon and mung beans

34:46.040 --> 34:48.500
to make him a cooling soup to reduce the heat.

34:48.560 --> 34:50.159
Our Brigade Commander actually finished it all

34:50.159 --> 34:51.520
and praised how good it tasted.

34:51.520 --> 34:54.179
How about I make one for Great-grandfather too?

34:54.280 --> 34:56.400
By the way, I'll use this winter melon and dried shrimp

34:56.400 --> 34:58.800
to make him a big stuffed Bun.

34:59.320 --> 35:00.240
Oh my goodness,

35:00.760 --> 35:02.020
you can also make Buns?

35:02.120 --> 35:03.400
What did you think?

35:03.600 --> 35:04.600
During the Mid-Autumn Festival,

35:04.600 --> 35:05.440
I was on the battlefield,

35:05.440 --> 35:06.840
and I used water caltrops

35:07.040 --> 35:08.920
to make water caltrop mooncakes for our Brigade Commander.

35:08.920 --> 35:09.680
He praised me,

35:09.680 --> 35:13.010
saying it was even better than the ones from Guanshengyuan.

35:15.280 --> 35:16.200
Don't.

35:22.680 --> 35:25.140
Great-grandfather still refuses to leave?

35:28.000 --> 35:29.800
He's been writing letters of appeal,

35:29.800 --> 35:32.480
but I went out looking for newspapers today.

35:33.600 --> 35:36.600
'Central Daily News' has already withdrawn to Wuhan.

35:37.560 --> 35:38.880
'Nanjing People's Daily'

35:38.880 --> 35:40.280
and other newspaper offices,

35:40.280 --> 35:41.400
have either suspended publication

35:41.400 --> 35:43.130
or simply have no one in charge.

35:43.720 --> 35:45.440
Actually, no matter how much he writes,

35:45.440 --> 35:47.240
there's nowhere to submit them.

35:47.400 --> 35:49.480
But seeing him like that today,

35:49.560 --> 35:51.600
I really don't know how to tell him.

35:53.760 --> 35:54.680
All right.

35:54.880 --> 35:55.740
Take your time.

35:56.880 --> 35:57.880
Madam.

35:58.720 --> 35:59.520
How about

36:00.040 --> 36:02.170
I try to persuade Great-grandfather?

36:02.840 --> 36:03.960
Do you have a way?

36:04.520 --> 36:05.360
Let me try.

36:05.600 --> 36:07.930
What if Great-grandfather listens to me?

36:09.360 --> 36:11.600
If you can persuade Great-grandfather,

36:11.600 --> 36:13.000
that would be wonderful.

36:14.520 --> 36:15.560
Then Madam,

36:16.120 --> 36:18.050
if I persuade Great-grandfather,

36:19.160 --> 36:20.720
can I make a small request?

36:20.840 --> 36:21.600
No.

36:21.960 --> 36:22.640
No.

36:23.920 --> 36:24.880
No.

36:25.040 --> 36:26.720
Then Madam, if not, I'll leave.

36:26.720 --> 36:27.280
Go.

36:27.440 --> 36:28.160
Wanfu,

36:29.600 --> 36:30.560
let him speak.

36:34.680 --> 36:35.360
Madam,

36:35.600 --> 36:38.460
if I can persuade Great-grandfather to go to Wuhan,

36:38.960 --> 36:40.290
can you take me with you?

36:40.680 --> 36:41.240
No,

36:41.400 --> 36:42.240
I know

36:42.480 --> 36:44.880
I shouldn't make requests for helping you.

36:45.040 --> 36:46.200
But Madam, you don't know,

36:46.200 --> 36:48.520
the price of a boat ticket to Wuhan these days

36:48.520 --> 36:50.280
is more than selling me three or four times over.

36:50.280 --> 36:51.760
I'm worried sick.

36:55.640 --> 36:56.640
Alright.

36:57.280 --> 36:59.720
If you can persuade Great-grandfather to go to Wuhan,

36:59.720 --> 37:00.760
we'll take you.

37:01.960 --> 37:03.240
Thank you, Madam.

37:03.760 --> 37:04.960
Then

37:05.760 --> 37:08.560
I'll make some buns for Great-grandfather first.

37:08.920 --> 37:09.960
Mrs. Liu,

37:10.120 --> 37:12.240
can you help me out?

37:19.280 --> 37:20.240
Alright.

37:20.760 --> 37:22.220
Go slice the winter melon.

37:25.120 --> 37:26.400
I'll go now.

38:14.120 --> 38:19.600
Who caused this disaster?

38:20.080 --> 38:23.810
Heaven does not repent of the disaster. Who caused this suffering?

38:24.040 --> 38:24.960
Read 'Tu'.

38:27.840 --> 38:30.970
This is Yan Zhenqing's 'Draft of a Requiem to My Nephew'.

38:33.000 --> 38:34.260
You don't eat or drink.

38:34.840 --> 38:36.480
You don't hide from the alarms.

38:36.480 --> 38:38.740
So you're practicing calligraphy here.

38:41.280 --> 38:42.400
What's the use

38:43.560 --> 38:45.240
of saying these things?

38:51.240 --> 38:52.970
Can this shoot down airplanes?

39:09.280 --> 39:11.440
I'm not afraid to tell you the truth.

39:11.760 --> 39:12.720
You

39:12.880 --> 39:14.680
are the most muddled

39:15.120 --> 39:17.640
and ungrateful person I've ever met.

39:21.240 --> 39:22.640
Why are you glaring at me?

39:23.160 --> 39:23.760
I'm afraid of guns and bullets,

39:23.760 --> 39:25.000
and I'm afraid of you glaring at me.

39:25.000 --> 39:26.960
If you have a great grievance,

39:27.240 --> 39:29.040
you should appeal it.

39:29.400 --> 39:31.120
You should curse.

39:31.840 --> 39:33.120
Just being a bully at home.

39:33.120 --> 39:35.720
Who are you scaring by not eating and drinking?

39:35.720 --> 39:37.120
All talk and no action.

39:37.360 --> 39:38.960
I don't see you really cursing.

39:38.960 --> 39:40.440
If you really want to curse,

39:40.440 --> 39:42.640
you have to let the right person hear it.

39:43.000 --> 39:44.400
I heard on the radio

39:44.840 --> 39:46.240
that the military and political officials

39:46.240 --> 39:48.000
have all moved to Wuhan.

39:48.440 --> 39:49.960
The main person has gone to Wuhan.

39:49.960 --> 39:52.160
You have to chase him to Wuhan and curse.

39:55.960 --> 39:57.490
We'll chase them and curse.

39:57.720 --> 40:00.200
Wherever they go, we'll curse.

40:00.400 --> 40:01.440
I'll help you curse.

40:01.440 --> 40:03.440
Who is loyal and who is treacherous,

40:03.440 --> 40:05.160
we must say it clearly

40:05.160 --> 40:06.000
and plainly.

40:06.200 --> 40:08.200
Otherwise, what does the storytelling say?

40:08.200 --> 40:08.880
That...

40:09.080 --> 40:09.840
That play...

40:09.880 --> 40:10.680
That one...

40:10.800 --> 40:12.600
The one where he cursed Cao Cao naked...

40:12.600 --> 40:13.520
What's it called?

40:13.520 --> 40:15.720
Mi Zhengping Curses the Thief Naked.

40:17.480 --> 40:18.880
That doesn't seem right.

40:19.120 --> 40:20.200
Called...

40:20.360 --> 40:21.420
What was it called?

40:24.120 --> 40:25.980
Beating the Drum and Cursing Cao.

40:26.280 --> 40:27.360
Great-grandfather,

40:27.360 --> 40:28.120
if Chairman Jiang

40:28.120 --> 40:30.040
doesn't clear our Brigade Commander's name,

40:30.040 --> 40:31.320
then he is Cao Cao.

40:31.760 --> 40:32.840
Then we have to do

40:33.560 --> 40:36.200
a 'Beating the Drum and Cursing Jiang'.

40:47.400 --> 40:50.280
Teach you treacherous dog a lesson,

40:50.680 --> 40:54.760
you will die without a good end.

40:57.040 --> 40:59.000
Pack my bags,

40:59.120 --> 41:01.640
travel by night,

41:02.280 --> 41:05.680
and go to Jingzhou.

41:06.960 --> 41:10.400
Wuhan, cursing Jiang.

41:25.160 --> 41:26.320
Zuliang, Zuliang.

41:27.000 --> 41:28.080
Where can I make a phone call?

41:28.080 --> 41:29.940
I need to call the Ministry of War.

41:30.320 --> 41:31.640
Since you can get out of bed,

41:31.640 --> 41:32.640
tomorrow at dawn,

41:32.840 --> 41:33.700
you must leave.

41:33.960 --> 41:35.520
I've altered your registration at the hospital.

41:35.520 --> 41:36.120
Remember,

41:36.440 --> 41:37.480
you've never been here.

41:37.480 --> 41:38.880
And I've never saved you.

41:40.080 --> 41:41.040
What do you mean?

41:41.640 --> 41:42.440
Dr. Luo.

41:42.720 --> 41:44.850
Is the medicine for patient 158 ready?

41:46.640 --> 41:47.440
I understand.

41:47.600 --> 41:48.320
In the end,

41:48.520 --> 41:49.880
everyone wants to save their own life.

41:49.880 --> 41:51.240
Our hospital received orders

41:51.240 --> 41:52.720
to be ready to retreat at any time.

41:52.720 --> 41:53.920
A platoon from the military police will come

41:53.920 --> 41:54.680
to assist us.

41:55.160 --> 41:56.640
Don't tell anyone

41:56.760 --> 41:57.440
who you are.

41:57.680 --> 41:59.080
What exactly is going on?

42:03.360 --> 42:04.200
See for yourself.
